contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionarypar|lorry}} '''Lorry''' may refer to: ==Transport== * [[Lorry (horse-drawn)]], a horse-drawn low-loading trolley * Lorry or [[truck]], a large motor vehicle * Lorry, or a mine car in USA: an open [[Gondola (rail)#Lorry|gondola]] (or railway car) with a tipping trough ==Structures== *[[Lorry, Frederiksberg]], a historic building complex in Copenhagen, Denmark ==In fiction== * [[Jarvis Lorry]], a fictional character in the Charles Dickens novel ''A Tale of Two Cities'' * ''[[The Lorry]]'', a 1977 French film ==Television== * [[Lorry (TV series)|''Lorry'' (TV series)]], Swedish comedy series from 1989 ==Nickname== *Lorry, the online handle of [[Michael Lawrie]] ==See also== * [[Lory (disambiguation)]] * [[Lori (disambiguation)]] * [[Loris (disambiguation)]] * [[Loris]], strepsirrhine primates of the subfamily Lorinae in family Lorisidae {{disambig}} [[de:Lore]]
